hum thay jinke saharay
woh howay na hamare
dobay dil ki naya paas huwe na hamare
kya mohabbat k waday kya wafa k eraday

kyu zindagi ki rah may majboor hogae itnay huway kharib hum door hoga a 
aisa nhi k humko koi bhi khushi nhi laykin yeh zindagi bhi koi zindagi nhi 
kyu is k faislay hame manzoor hoga a 
itnay kharib huee hum door hoga a 
